name: Photo-rater-support
body:
# Photo Rater 

See how many score you can get with your photo
Upload a photo or take one from camera and let this app calculate a score for you.

## Key Features
* Upload photo from photo gallery or camera
* Recognize information from uploaded photo as tag
* Calculate total score from each given tag
* Share your photo score with your friend on Facebook
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
